{"tid":1588251,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［戰術討論］要唔要試吓用電筒","createTime":"2019-09-22T17:24:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T15:16:11.000Z","uid":310821,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"093119db230a2d9669ffa124a4b0f1cebc66dce5","tid":1588251,"uid":310821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T17:24:32.000Z","msg":"P牌第一次開po 開得唔好屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n眼見依家有支雷射筆喺身就告藏有攻擊性武器<br />\n用嚟照狗又告襲警  雷射筆已經無當初咁有用<br />\n之前都見過有巴打講過唔好再用雷射筆[url]<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1517004/page/1[url]\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1517004/page/1[url]</a><br />\n<br />\n既然雷射筆帶又告用又告<br />\n點解唔用電筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n狗個邊成日都用電筒照9記者<br />\n咁如果我地用照lazer方式照返狗又可唔可行<br />\n又可以阻止狗個cam影到手足<br />\n如果佢咁都告襲警 咁平時照記者咪普通襲擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外電筒喺身唔犯法掛<br />\n返屋企條路黑要用<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行夜山要用<br />\n行完夜山唔記得執走唔比咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[member]電筒仲有多個用途 可以現場發掘下 打中關節應該都幾痛[member]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想集思廣益下 睇下有無用<br />\n另外係其他巴打好早已經講過電筒呢個方法<br />\n以下為部分<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1250235/page/1[url]\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1250235/page/1[url]</a><br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1380304/page/1[url]\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1380304/page/1[url]</a><br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1331486/page/1[url]\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1331486/page/1[url]</a><br />\n<br />\n最後希望大家覺得有用就推<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5871c6ad88f2ca6c46454b4018253b691901a5","tid":1588251,"uid":310821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T17:24:50.000Z",